job_description:
• Minimum 6 years of experience is a must.
  • Strong Python Programming skill.
  • Experience with Python Flask would be highly desired.
  • Experience with Git and should be able to commit the code.
  • Expert knowledge of SQL.
  • Work experience of IDE (any) PyCharm, visual source code.
  • Self-motivated with strong development skills and the ability to learn new technologies .
  • Ability to handle complex scenarios, multiple tasks, challenging priorities and set schedule to meet deliverables with positive attitude and flexibility .
  • Ability to work independently, collaborate as a member of a team, and build strong working relationships with partners and stakeholders .
  • Ability to effectively communicate with internal and external technology teams
